stateDiagram-v2
    [HealthTech_EMR_Sync] --> Idle
    Idle --> Gated : Session/day filters & range gate pass
    Gated --> SignalCheck : Close[HealthTech_EMR_Sync] vs Close[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    SignalCheck --> EntryBUY : Close[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer] >= Close[HealthTech_PatientRecords] AND no SELLs
    SignalCheck --> EntrySELL : Close[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer] < Close[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] AND no BUYs
    EntryBUY --> BasketManage
    EntrySELL --> BasketManage
    BasketManage --> AddMore : |price - last_entry| >= Step AND count < MaxTrades
    AddMore --> BasketManage
    BasketManage --> SyncTP : compute avg price; set TP = avg ± TP_pts
    SyncTP --> Idle
    Idle --> EquityStop : floating P/L < 0 AND |P/L| > (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)
    Idle --> HiddenTP : Hidden_TP basket profit reached
    Idle --> DailyTarget : Use_Daily_Target and daily ≥ Daily_Target
    EquityStop --> Flat
    HiddenTP --> Flat
    DailyTarget --> Flat
    Flat --> Idle
